<plot>The movie begins with the death of Varma (Murali) a senior government official who was about to on the verge of making a major anti-corruption bust. The case is handed over to Chandrashekharan IPS (Suresh Gopi) who goes by the nickname of "The Tiger". A turning point comes in the movie when a TV journalist Suhara (Gopika) disappears along with her Cameraman. Chandrashekhar finds a link between both the cases and is out to catch the mysterious assassin who is responsible for the death of Varma.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?596023</url></doc>
